fields.name: C2 CARGO
fields.description:
The LK2 Cargo Pants are designed with a customdeveloped synthetic fabric and featured a mesh lining, extended inseam for stacking throughout, with cargo pocket at side seam, an elastic waistband, and finished with % bungee cords that run halflength of the garment that each have 5 black plastic toggles to help with the stacking throughout. These pants also feature a zipper design around the knee, you can zip out the bungee lower part to change it as a pair of shorts.

Details

  • relaxed fit
  • 5 Pockets
  • 100% nylon
  • elastic waistband
  • fits truetosize, go one size up for baggy fit
  • model is 5'11(180cm), 154 lbs(70kg) and wears a size 30

*for tight fit, please go for smaller
